"Yes sir." Cyclonus said as he sent a few commands back to Scourge and
a few other of the Predacons. Swiftly the shuttle and most of the
Predacons move in the direction that Hydras indicated.

"I am with you Sire." Inferno, Hydras' self appointed guardian said as
he moved up on the other side of Hydras.

Scourge and a couple of sweeps moved up to fall in behind Cyclonus and
Hydras, giving him a complete complement should he need it.

"We have everything under control." Cyclonus said. "However what about
the spy that we sent into the Ark. He may need assisance in getting
out. No doubt the Maximals are going back there even now to try to
free thier captured comrades. I got a mesage that He no longer can
hold Nightlight over thier head, some how the maximals were able to
rescue her and finish rebooting her systems."

(TAG)
